# Project Structure Guide

- The main app entry point is [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx), which sets up global providers, navigation, and meta tags.
- Onboarding flow is implemented in [app/onboarding/page.tsx](mdc:app/onboarding/page.tsx).
- User profile and preferences are managed in [app/profile/page.tsx](mdc:app/profile/page.tsx).
- The main user type and authentication logic are in [context/auth-context.tsx](mdc:context/auth-context.tsx).
- Admin dashboard and related features are in the `app/admin/` directory.
- Global styles are loaded from [app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css).
- Open Graph and other meta tags should be added in [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) inside the `<head>` block.
